on our conversation from two days ago.

43:29.390 --> 43:30.550
Is now a good time?

43:31.150 --> 43:32.515
I ought to kick your ass.

43:32.610 --> 43:34.510
Your insurer will likely see

43:34.610 --> 43:37.738
that the damage was not caused
by an act of God,

43:37.820 --> 43:39.230
but a large boat.

43:39.820 --> 43:41.651
And if he's a suspicious type...

43:41.740 --> 43:43.776
You know those insurance fuckers.

43:43.870 --> 43:48.159
