-It's the best we can do.

46:08.640 --> 46:11.006
You're a very persuasive woman,
Wendy Byrde.

46:11.760 --> 46:12.966
What about my boat?

46:13.560 --> 46:15.175
That's Why you have insurance.

46:16.270 --> 46:19.728
Hey, for the record,
I didn't close down your businesses.

46:20.520 --> 46:22.568
Someone's got you in their crosshairs.

46:23.190 --> 46:24.600
