46:44.210 --> 46:45.916
-and a shit-ton of clock repair.
-Can you hold on for one second?

46:46.010 --> 46:47.295
-And I figure we can make up...
-Let me...

46:47.380 --> 46:49.462
-Hey, Ruth.
-...for most of the laundering we've
lost, with the businesses shut down,
just on repairs alone.

46:51.720 --> 46:53.551
Just stop for a second, okay?

46:53.640 --> 46:56.473
