47:11.240 --> 47:14.573
No, I am not. The gaming commission
is launching, uh, an investigation.

47:14.660 --> 47:17.823
We can't have a convicted felon
on any paperwork. That's all.

47:17.910 --> 47:19.662
You're fucking firing me.

47:19.750 --> 47:21.661
_ Just in name. _
You're still gonna manage the strip club.

47:21.750 --> 47:23.081
You're still gonna get paid. We just...

47:23.170 --> 47:25.582
We need to have somebody else
be the face of the place.

47:26.800 --> 47:27.664
Okay?

47:28.590 --> 47:30.080
-I get it.
-Good.

47:38.390 --> 47:40.017
[Rachel]
Why are you yelling at me?

47:40.100 --> 47:42.182
Because he could've found the Wire.

47:42.270 --> 47:43.180
He didn't.

47:43.690 --> 47:45.260
How the fuck do you know?

47:48.820 --> 47:52.563
-Hey, look, I am not cut out for this.
-I don't care.

47:56.370 --> 47:58.577
It just makes me hate myself so much.

48:11.430 --> 48:13.216
Do better than you've been doing.

48:22.100 --> 48:23.977
[Jacob] Here's to our working partnership.

48:24.480 --> 48:26.857
-[Marty] Yeah. Sure. Cheers.
-[clinking]

48:26.940 --> 48:30.182
Absolutely, and to us
being up and running again.

48:33.660 --> 48:35.560
We appreciate you understanding

48:35.660 --> 48:38.902
